summary: One of my personal objectives is to be a professional technologist. I have gotten a degree at Polytechnic School in Delft, went o the University of Amsterdam and became a Professor of Chemistry, Mineralogy, and Geology. I've obtained a doctors degree in Holland. I've earned a Nobel prize and I was actually the first dutch chemist to have earned one. I am founder of the discoveries of chemical kinetics, chemical equilibrium, osmotic pressure, and stereo chemistry.
